activate(uint256).details: Activate specific beneficiary by index_. Only active beneficiaries can claim tokens.

activateAdvisor().details: Activate all of advisor beneficiaries. Only active beneficiaries can claim tokens.

activateAll().details: Activate all of beneficiaries. Only active beneficiaries can claim tokens.

activateIncentives().details: Activate all of incentives beneficiaries. Only active beneficiaries can claim tokens.

activateLiquidity().details: Activate all of liquidity beneficiaries. Only active beneficiaries can claim tokens.

activateMarketing().details: Activate all of marketing beneficiaries. Only active beneficiaries can claim tokens.

activatePrivateSale().details: Activate all of private sale beneficiaries. Only active beneficiaries can claim tokens.

activatePublicSale().details: Activate all of public sale beneficiaries. Only active beneficiaries can claim tokens.

activateReserve().details: Activate all of reserve beneficiaries. Only active beneficiaries can claim tokens.

activateTeam().details: Activate all of team beneficiaries. Only active beneficiaries can claim tokens.

addBeneficiary(address,uint256,uint256,u.details: Add beneficiary to vesting plan using default basis.

params.participant_: specific type of {Participant}. Waring: Convert vesting monthly to duration carefully eg: vesting in 9 months => duration = 8 months = 8 * 30 * 24 * 60 * 60
params.tgeAmount_: an amount of tokens will be vested at tge.
params.totalAmount_: total amount of tokens will be vested.

params.basis_: basis duration for linear vesting. Waring: Convert vesting monthly to duration carefully eg: vesting in 9 months => duration = 8 months = 8 * 30 * 24 * 60 * 60
params.tgeAmount_: an amount of tokens will be vested at tge.
params.totalAmount_: total amount of tokens will be vested.

constructor.details: Sets the value for {token}. This value are immutable: it can only be set once during construction.

getAllBeneficiaries().details: Get all beneficiaries, only called by owner

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

potentialOwner().details: Returns the address of the current potentialOwner.

releasable(uint256).details: Returns the total releasable amount of tokens for the specific beneficiary by index.

release(uint256).details: Release all releasable amount of tokens for the sepecific beneficiary by index. Emits a {TokensReleased} event.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions anymore. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby removing any functionality that is only available to the owner.

revoke(uint256).details: Revoke specific beneficiary by index_. Revoked beneficiaries cannot vest tokens anymore.

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

withdraw(uint256).details: Withdraw revoked tokens out of contract. Withdraw amount of tokens upto revoked amount.
